                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Defensive Assist: Desperate Defense<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the character on field is about to be attacked, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Parries the enemy's attack, dealing massive Daze.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the character on field is about to be attacked, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Parries the enemy's attack, dealing massive Daze.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Assist Follow-Up: Shadow Strike<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> after a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Defensive Assist</span> to activate:<br/>Charge and slash enemies in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
