                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Warmup Sparks<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to 4 slashes, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to 4 slashes, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Fire Suppression<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> at the right moment to activate:<br/>Launches a stronger slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>When <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span> is guaranteed to trigger, pressing <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> when the attack is about to end speeds up the transition into the next hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>When <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span> is guaranteed to trigger, the 5th hit of the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> string unlocks. Activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span> powers up her next <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> 5th hit. A strengthened <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> 5th hit will consume all remaining guaranteed <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span> activations to deal additional <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span> per activation spent.<br/>After triggering a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span>, the current Basic Attack hit count is retained for 5s. After performing a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, pressing <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> resumes the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> from the retained hit count.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> at the right moment to activate:<br/>Launches a stronger slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>When <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span> is guaranteed to trigger, pressing <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> when the attack is about to end speeds up the transition into the next hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>When <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span> is guaranteed to trigger, the 5th hit of the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> string unlocks. Activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span> powers up her next <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> 5th hit. A strengthened <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> 5th hit will consume all remaining guaranteed <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span> activations to deal additional <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span> per activation spent.<br/>After triggering a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span>, the current Basic Attack hit count is retained for 5s. After performing a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, pressing <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> resumes the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> from the retained hit count.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Fire Assault<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate: <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Charge</span><br/>Release <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> while Basic Attack: Fire Charge is activated to launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Assault</span>.<br/>If attacked by an enemy during <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Assault</span> or the moment <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Charge</span> is activated, a Block Counter can be triggered, negating that instance of DMG and granting 3 guaranteed triggers of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span>. Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to follow up with the 3rd hit of a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>, up to 8 times.<br/>While charging, tilting the joystick launches <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Blazing Rush</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate: <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Charge</span><br/>Release <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> while Basic Attack: Fire Charge is activated to launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Assault</span>.<br/>If attacked by an enemy during <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Assault</span> or the moment <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Charge</span> is activated, a Block Counter can be triggered, negating that instance of DMG and granting 3 guaranteed triggers of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span>. Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to follow up with the 3rd hit of a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>, up to 8 times.<br/>While charging, tilting the joystick launches <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Blazing Rush</span>.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
