            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Raging Fire<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Slashes enemies nearby, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Slashes enemies nearby, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Fervent Fire<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Executes a powerful slash against enemies nearby, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>After using this skill, Soldier 11's <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attacks</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dash Attacks</span> are guaranteed to trigger <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span> for up to 30s or 8 times.<br/>After using this skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to immediately follow up with the 4th hit of a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>Soldier 11 enters the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Alert Stance</span> after using this skill. While in <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Alert Stance</span>, if hit during a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>, triggers <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Charge</span> to block the attack, followed by <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Assault</span>. After <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Assault</span> is performed, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to resume <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> from the retained Basic Attack hit count.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Executes a powerful slash against enemies nearby, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>After using this skill, Soldier 11's <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attacks</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dash Attacks</span> are guaranteed to trigger <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fire Suppression</span> for up to 30s or 8 times.<br/>After using this skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to immediately follow up with the 4th hit of a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>Soldier 11 enters the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Alert Stance</span> after using this skill. While in <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Alert Stance</span>, if hit during a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>, triggers <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Charge</span> to block the attack, followed by <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Assault</span>. After <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fire Assault</span> is performed, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to resume <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> from the retained Basic Attack hit count.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
