            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Cease Thoughts<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches enemies in front into the air, dealing <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches enemies in front into the air, dealing <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Frost Coil<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Perform two consecutive upward strikes, then release an icy mist, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>If EX Special Attack: Frost Coil hits an enemy, Yidhari recovers HP at the end of the skill equal to 33% of her missing HP.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Perform two consecutive upward strikes, then release an icy mist, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>If EX Special Attack: Frost Coil hits an enemy, Yidhari recovers HP at the end of the skill equal to 33% of her missing HP.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Surging Cold, Crushing Pursuit<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> or <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> while charging or spinning during <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span>, or press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> while holding <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches enemies in front into the air, dealing <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>When the skill's attack collides with an enemy's attack, it triggers Surging Cold.<br/>If the skill hits a Stunned enemy, and with sufficient Adrenaline, it triggers Crushing Pursuit.<br/>Triggering Surging Cold or Crushing Pursuit instantly raises the charge level to maximum.<br/>During this skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> and Yidhari will immediately unleash the finishing slam of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span> based on the current charge level.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> or <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> while charging or spinning during <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span>, or press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> while holding <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches enemies in front into the air, dealing <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>When the skill's attack collides with an enemy's attack, it triggers Surging Cold.<br/>If the skill hits a Stunned enemy, and with sufficient Adrenaline, it triggers Crushing Pursuit.<br/>Triggering Surging Cold or Crushing Pursuit instantly raises the charge level to maximum.<br/>During this skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> and Yidhari will immediately unleash the finishing slam of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span> based on the current charge level.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Glacial Crush<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When triggering Surging Cold or Crushing Pursuit, and with enough Adrenaline, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> or <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Dash forward with an upward attack, then leap into the air before delivering a powerful downward smash, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Glacial Crush</span> hits an enemy, Yidhari heals at the end of the skill for 33% of her missing HP.<br/>If the skill is used after Surging Cold, it grants an additional 15 Adrenaline. This effect can trigger once every 1s.<br/>After using this skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to immediately unleash the finishing slam of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span> based on the current charge level.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When triggering Surging Cold or Crushing Pursuit, and with enough Adrenaline, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> or <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Dash forward with an upward attack, then leap into the air before delivering a powerful downward smash, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Glacial Crush</span> hits an enemy, Yidhari heals at the end of the skill for 33% of her missing HP.<br/>If the skill is used after Surging Cold, it grants an additional 15 Adrenaline. This effect can trigger once every 1s.<br/>After using this skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to immediately unleash the finishing slam of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span> based on the current charge level.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
