            "3": {
                "skillId": 3,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Chain Attack: Frostbound Oath<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>Unleash a powerful strike against enemies in a small area ahead, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>If inside <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, tentacles join in the assault, further enhancing the skill's power.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>Unleash a powerful strike against enemies in a small area ahead, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>If inside <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, tentacles join in the assault, further enhancing the skill's power.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Ether Veil: Wellspring<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Decibel Rating is at <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Maximum</span>, the final hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Frost Coil</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Glacial Crush</span>, and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack: Frostbound Oath</span> will consume 3,000 Decibels to activate an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>. While <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> is active, all squad members' Max HP increase by 5% for 30s. Repeated triggers extend the duration, up to a maximum of 300s.<br/>While Yidhari is within <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, the charge speed of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span> increases, and HP is consumed faster during charging.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Decibel Rating is at <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Maximum</span>, the final hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Frost Coil</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Glacial Crush</span>, and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack: Frostbound Oath</span> will consume 3,000 Decibels to activate an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>. While <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> is active, all squad members' Max HP increase by 5% for 30s. Repeated triggers extend the duration, up to a maximum of 300s.<br/>While Yidhari is within <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, the charge speed of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span> increases, and HP is consumed faster during charging.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Ultimate: Final Act - Crossing the River of Regret<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->After Yidhari expends Decibels to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> within 30s to activate:<br/>Deliver a powerful strike to enemies in a large area ahead, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>Each time Yidhari expends Decibels to activate an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, she can use <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate: Final Act - Crossing the River of Regret</span> once.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->After Yidhari expends Decibels to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> within 30s to activate:<br/>Deliver a powerful strike to enemies in a large area ahead, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>Each time Yidhari expends Decibels to activate an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, she can use <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate: Final Act - Crossing the River of Regret</span> once.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
