        "coreSkill": {
            "desc": [
                "<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2.5 text-sm leading-4\"><!--[--><div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Core Passive: Dreamscape Collection<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Yidhari gains extra Sheer Force based on her Max HP, with every 1 point of Max HP increasing Sheer Force by 0.1.<br/>All <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span> dealt by Yidhari deals is Sheer DMG, ignoring enemy DEF and using her Sheer Force stat as the DMG Multiplier. When Yidhari enters battle, she immediately gains 60 Adrenaline. In Investigation Zone Mode, this effect can trigger once every 180s.<br/>Yidhari's skill DMG increases as her current HP percentage decreases.<br/>When her HP falls below 50%, the buff reaches its maximum value, increasing her DMG by up to <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">100%</span>. Once her HP is restored to 50%, the maximum bonus remains for 5s thereafter.<br/>Yidhari gains fewer Decibels from landing skills. Instead, she gains Decibels as her HP decreases, with every 1% HP lost granting 10 Decibels.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div><div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Additional Ability: Narrative Completion<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When another character in your squad is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Stun</span> or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Support</span> character:<br/>When Yidhari's HP falls below 50%, CRIT DMG increases by 30% and DMG taken is reduced by 25%.<br/>While Yidhari is within <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, she gains the following additional effect:<br/>After the level 3 charged attack of Yidhari's <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace</span> or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Glacial Crush</span>, an icy tentacle is summoned to attack, dealing extra damage. This effect can trigger once every 12s.<br/>The above skill is considered an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, the DMG multiplier increases based on the EX Special Attack's level.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div><!--]--><!-- --></div>"
            ],
            "coreGrowthStat": {
                "20101": 48000,
                "12101": 25
            }
        }
    },
