        "skillKit": {
            "0": {
                "skillId": 0,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Kazahana<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to five slashes ahead, the first two deal <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>, and the last three deal <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Frost DMG</span>.<br/>Block enemy attacks during the 5th hit of the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to five slashes ahead, the first two deal <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>, and the last three deal <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Frost DMG</span>.<br/>Block enemy attacks during the 5th hit of the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Shimotsuki<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With at least 2 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Hoshimi Miyabi sheaths her blade, enters <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shimotsuki Stance</span> and starts to charge up. Every level of charge will consume 2 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span>, up to a maximum of three levels of charge.<br/>When releasing <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/>, or when <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span> is completely depleted, Hoshimi Miyabi will draw her blade and unleash a powerful slash ahead based on the current charge level, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Frost DMG</span>. She then exits <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shimotsuki Stance</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable during <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shimotsuki Stance</span>.<br/>Hoshimi Miyabi can have up to 6 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span>. Upon entering the battlefield, Hoshimi Miyabi immediately obtains 3 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With at least 2 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Hoshimi Miyabi sheaths her blade, enters <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shimotsuki Stance</span> and starts to charge up. Every level of charge will consume 2 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span>, up to a maximum of three levels of charge.<br/>When releasing <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/>, or when <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span> is completely depleted, Hoshimi Miyabi will draw her blade and unleash a powerful slash ahead based on the current charge level, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Frost DMG</span>. She then exits <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shimotsuki Stance</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable during <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shimotsuki Stance</span>.<br/>Hoshimi Miyabi can have up to 6 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span>. Upon entering the battlefield, Hoshimi Miyabi immediately obtains 3 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fallen Frost</span>.<!-- --></span>"
