                "skillId": 0,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Smash 'n' Bash<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to 4 strikes, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>When Koleda has the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Furnace Fire</span> effect, she can launch an enhanced <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> after the 2nd hit, consuming the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Furnace Fire</span> effect and dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>When Koleda and Ben are deployed together, executing an enhanced <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> will trigger a coordinated attack from both, further increasing the move's power;<br/>Koleda is invulnerable during the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack's</span> 4th hit and enhanced <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to 4 strikes, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>When Koleda has the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Furnace Fire</span> effect, she can launch an enhanced <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> after the 2nd hit, consuming the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Furnace Fire</span> effect and dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>When Koleda and Ben are deployed together, executing an enhanced <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span> will trigger a coordinated attack from both, further increasing the move's power;<br/>Koleda is invulnerable during the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack's</span> 4th hit and enhanced <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<!-- --></span>"
