            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Fiscal Fist<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Ben lifts his weapon, blocking the enemy's attack before unleashing a forward strike, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>. Successfully blocking an attack enhances the power of this skill and triggers Block Counter, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to remain in the Blocking stance.<br/>While in the Blocking stance, Ben gains a Shield that weakens over time.<br/>After leaving the blocking stance, the Shield is removed and recovers over time.<br/>The Shield cannot exceed 16% of Ben's Max HP.<br/>Ben is invulnerable when activating Block.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while launching strikes.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Ben lifts his weapon, blocking the enemy's attack before unleashing a forward strike, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>. Successfully blocking an attack enhances the power of this skill and triggers Block Counter, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to remain in the Blocking stance.<br/>While in the Blocking stance, Ben gains a Shield that weakens over time.<br/>After leaving the blocking stance, the Shield is removed and recovers over time.<br/>The Shield cannot exceed 16% of Ben's Max HP.<br/>Ben is invulnerable when activating Block.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while launching strikes.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Cashflow Counter<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Ben lifts his weapon, blocking the enemy's attacks before unleashing a forward strike, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>. Successfully blocking an attack enhances the power of this skill and triggers Block Counter, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to remain in the Blocking stance.<br/>While in the Blocking stance, Ben gains a Shield that weakens over time.<br/>After leaving the blocking stance, the Shield is removed and recovers over time.<br/>The Shield cannot exceed 16% of Ben's Max HP.<br/>When this skill is activated, the Shield is restored to its maximum value.<br/>After activating the skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> again to follow up with a powerful forward strike, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Ben is invulnerable when activating Block.<br/>Ben is invulnerable while launching strikes.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Ben lifts his weapon, blocking the enemy's attacks before unleashing a forward strike, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>. Successfully blocking an attack enhances the power of this skill and triggers Block Counter, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to remain in the Blocking stance.<br/>While in the Blocking stance, Ben gains a Shield that weakens over time.<br/>After leaving the blocking stance, the Shield is removed and recovers over time.<br/>The Shield cannot exceed 16% of Ben's Max HP.<br/>When this skill is activated, the Shield is restored to its maximum value.<br/>After activating the skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> again to follow up with a powerful forward strike, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Ben is invulnerable when activating Block.<br/>Ben is invulnerable while launching strikes.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
