            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: V-Form Sunrise Uppercut<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Strikes enemies in front with an uppercut, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<br/>Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> during a shuffle dodge to activate:<br/>Strike forward with a series of punches, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>This skill will not interrupt the combo count for <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attacks</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Strikes enemies in front with an uppercut, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<br/>Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> during a shuffle dodge to activate:<br/>Strike forward with a series of punches, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>This skill will not interrupt the combo count for <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attacks</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: V-Form Sunrise Uppercut - Full Distance<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Strikes enemies in front with a powerful uppercut, leaping into the air and dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>During the move, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> again to spend additional Energy to perform a powerful follow-up attack, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill<br/>After using the move, press or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to transition to the 4th hit of the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>During the shuffle dodge, with enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Perform a powerful combo punch forward, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>. Using this skill will not break the combo count for <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attacks</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>After the attack, press or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to immediately transition into the 5th hit of the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>. <!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Strikes enemies in front with a powerful uppercut, leaping into the air and dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>During the move, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> again to spend additional Energy to perform a powerful follow-up attack, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill<br/>After using the move, press or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to transition to the 4th hit of the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>During the shuffle dodge, with enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Perform a powerful combo punch forward, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>. Using this skill will not break the combo count for <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attacks</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>After the attack, press or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to immediately transition into the 5th hit of the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>. <!-- --></span>"
                ],
