            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Obstruction Removal<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Throws a grenade forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>During the skill, drag the joystick to reposition in that direction.<br/>When activated via consuming <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span>, dodge incoming enemy attacks.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Throws a grenade forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>During the skill, drag the joystick to reposition in that direction.<br/>When activated via consuming <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span>, dodge incoming enemy attacks.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Supercharged Obstruction Removal<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Leaps into the air and throws two grenades forward, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>During the skill, drag the joystick to change directions.<br/>If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span> reaches max stacks, throws an additional Vortex Cluster Grenade, generating an electromagnetic field at the point of detonation that pulls in enemies and deals <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Leaps into the air and throws two grenades forward, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>During the skill, drag the joystick to change directions.<br/>If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span> reaches max stacks, throws an additional Vortex Cluster Grenade, generating an electromagnetic field at the point of detonation that pulls in enemies and deals <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Pulse<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Activating an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span> grants 25 stacks of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pulse</span> (max 25 stacks). When gaining <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span>, consumes 1 stack of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pulse</span>.<br/>After consuming <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pulse</span> to obtain 8 stacks of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span>, the next grenade throw includes an additional Pulse Grenade. If it hits an enemy suffering <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether</span>, <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric</span>, <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire</span>, <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical</span>, or <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice</span> Anomaly, it triggers <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Abloom</span>: deals an additional instance of DMG equal to <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">560%</span>/<span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">280%</span>/<span style=\"color: #FF5521\">700%</span>/<span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">50%</span>/<span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">70%</span> of the original Anomaly's DMG.<br/>While in the Pulse state, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Obstruction Removal - Cycle</span> is unlocked.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Activating an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span> grants 25 stacks of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pulse</span> (max 25 stacks). When gaining <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span>, consumes 1 stack of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pulse</span>.<br/>After consuming <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pulse</span> to obtain 8 stacks of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span>, the next grenade throw includes an additional Pulse Grenade. If it hits an enemy suffering <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether</span>, <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric</span>, <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire</span>, <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical</span>, or <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice</span> Anomaly, it triggers <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Abloom</span>: deals an additional instance of DMG equal to <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">560%</span>/<span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">280%</span>/<span style=\"color: #FF5521\">700%</span>/<span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">50%</span>/<span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">70%</span> of the original Anomaly's DMG.<br/>While in the Pulse state, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Obstruction Removal - Cycle</span> is unlocked.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Obstruction Removal - Cycle<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the Pulse state, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Repeatedly hurls grenades forward during the skill, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span> and granting 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span> stack each time grenades are thrown.<br/>During the skill, tilt the joystick to reposition and dodge enemy attacks.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the Pulse state, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Repeatedly hurls grenades forward during the skill, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span> and granting 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Zap</span> stack each time grenades are thrown.<br/>During the skill, tilt the joystick to reposition and dodge enemy attacks.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
