            "23101": 0,
            "30501": 12000
        },
        "skillKit": {
            "0": {
                "skillId": 0,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Feathered Strike<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to four attacks in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> and <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>After triggering the fourth attack, enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Noblewoman</span> state.<br/>With <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span> available, holding <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> during the fourth attack will activate the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to four attacks in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> and <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>After triggering the fourth attack, enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Noblewoman</span> state.<br/>With <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span> available, holding <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> during the fourth attack will activate the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Noblewoman - Waltz<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> while in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Noblewoman</span> state to activate:<br/>Dash forward with an attack that deals <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span> and restores 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feather</span> upon hitting an enemy.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>If a Perfect Dodge is triggered during the dash, gain 1 additional <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feather</span>.<br/>If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span> are available after the skill, enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state, which can be canceled by holding <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> when the skill is used.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> while in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Noblewoman</span> state to activate:<br/>Dash forward with an attack that deals <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span> and restores 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feather</span> upon hitting an enemy.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>If a Perfect Dodge is triggered during the dash, gain 1 additional <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feather</span>.<br/>If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span> are available after the skill, enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state, which can be canceled by holding <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> when the skill is used.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Fluttering Frock - Suspension<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> while in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state to activate:<br/>Attack an area ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>After activation, this skill consumes all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span>, and each one consumed grants 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Guard Feather</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>When switching characters during the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state, Vivian will automatically perform <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fluttering Frock - Suspension</span>.<br/>While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to exit the state.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> while in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state to activate:<br/>Attack an area ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>After activation, this skill consumes all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span>, and each one consumed grants 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Guard Feather</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>When switching characters during the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state, Vivian will automatically perform <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fluttering Frock - Suspension</span>.<br/>While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to exit the state.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Featherbloom<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->After any squad member hits a target with an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, Vivian will consume 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Guard Feather</span> to launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Featherbloom</span> against the target, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>, triggering at most once per use of a skill. This effect can trigger even while Vivian is off-field.<br/>A maximum of 5 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Guard Feathers</span> can be stored.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->After any squad member hits a target with an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, Vivian will consume 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Guard Feather</span> to launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Featherbloom</span> against the target, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>, triggering at most once per use of a skill. This effect can trigger even while Vivian is off-field.<br/>A maximum of 5 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Guard Feathers</span> can be stored.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
