            "6": {
                "skillId": 6,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Quick Assist: Frostwing Guard<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the active character is launched, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches an attack on enemies ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> and <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>After the skill activates, enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Noblewoman</span> state.<br/>With <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span> available, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> during skill activation to enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the active character is launched, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches an attack on enemies ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> and <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>After the skill activates, enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Noblewoman</span> state.<br/>With <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span> available, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> during skill activation to enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Defensive Assist: Silver Umbrella Formation<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the on-field character is about to be attacked, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Parries the enemy's attack, dealing massive Daze.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the on-field character is about to be attacked, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Parries the enemy's attack, dealing massive Daze.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Assist Follow-Up: Featherblade Execution<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> after a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Defensive Assist</span> to activate:<br/>Launch an attack at enemies ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span> and gaining 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>After the skill activates enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state, which can be canceled by holding <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> during the skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> after a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Defensive Assist</span> to activate:<br/>Launch an attack at enemies ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span> and gaining 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<br/>After the skill activates enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Fluttering Frock</span> state, which can be canceled by holding <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> during the skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
