        "coreSkill": {
            "desc": [
                "<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2.5 text-sm leading-4\"><!--[--><div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Core Passive: Dirge of Destiny<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Featherbloom</span> hits a target that is suffering from an <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether</span>, <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric</span>, <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire</span>, <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical</span>, or <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice</span> Anomaly, it will trigger <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Abloom</span>, dealing additional Attribute Anomaly DMG. The additional DMG is <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">6.15%</span>/<span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">3.2%</span>/<span style=\"color: #FF5521\">8%</span>/<span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">0.75%</span>/<span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">1.08%</span> per 10 points of Anomaly Proficiency of the original Anomaly DMG.<br/>When <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Fluttering Frock - Suspension</span> or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Featherbloom</span> hits a target suffering any Attribute Anomaly, it will inflict <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Vivian's Prophecy</span>, causing the target to take <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span> equal to 55% of Vivian's ATK every 0.55s. This DMG can trigger additional DMG from Attribute Anomalies. <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Vivian's Prophecy</span> ends when the target is no longer suffering an Attribute Anomaly.<br/>When entering the battlefield, Vivian gains 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Flight Feathers</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div><div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Additional Ability: Prophetic Tears<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When another character in your squad is an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Anomaly</span> character or shares the same attribute:<br/>Whenever another squad member applies an Attribute Anomaly to an enemy, Vivian will consume 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Guard Feather</span> to launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Featherbloom</span> on the target. This can trigger once every 0.5s.<br/><span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Corruption</span> DMG dealt by all squad members and the <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Corruption</span> status' <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Disorder</span> DMG increases by <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">12%</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div><!--]--><!-- --></div>"
            ],
            "coreGrowthStat": {
                "31401": 12,
                "12101": 25
            }
        }
    },
