                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Glacial Judgment<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches up to five slashes forward, the first dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>, and the following four <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches up to five slashes forward, the first dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>, and the following four <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Final Verdict<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>After getting ready, Zhao starts charging up, then launches a forward slash on release, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>While charging, Zhao accumulates up to 5s of charge time. When the Finishing Move of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span> hits, the stored charge time is consumed to deal additional DMG. For every 1 second of charge time, Zhao deals <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">24%</span> of Max HP as additional DMG.<br/>When Zhao is in any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, if she gets switched out while charging, the charge can continue.<br/>If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are maxed out when the skill activates, all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are consumed to trigger <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> and a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>. If a squadmate is then switched in via <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, Zhao automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span> and begins charging.<br/>During skill activation, Anti-Interrupt level increases, and DMG taken is reduced by 40%.<br/>While not the currently controlled character, the character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>After getting ready, Zhao starts charging up, then launches a forward slash on release, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>While charging, Zhao accumulates up to 5s of charge time. When the Finishing Move of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span> hits, the stored charge time is consumed to deal additional DMG. For every 1 second of charge time, Zhao deals <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">24%</span> of Max HP as additional DMG.<br/>When Zhao is in any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, if she gets switched out while charging, the charge can continue.<br/>If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are maxed out when the skill activates, all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are consumed to trigger <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> and a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>. If a squadmate is then switched in via <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, Zhao automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span> and begins charging.<br/>During skill activation, Anti-Interrupt level increases, and DMG taken is reduced by 40%.<br/>While not the currently controlled character, the character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
