            "6": {
                "skillId": 6,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Entry Skill: Burst of Frost<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Zhao has maximum <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span>, and is in combat, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches consecutive attacks forward, followed by a slash, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are consumed to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> is triggered. If a squadmate is then switched in via <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, Zhao automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span> and begins charging.<br/>Activating this skill is considered as activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Zhao has maximum <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span>, and is in combat, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches consecutive attacks forward, followed by a slash, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are consumed to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> is triggered. If a squadmate is then switched in via <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, Zhao automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span> and begins charging.<br/>Activating this skill is considered as activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Quick Assist: Patch the Gaps<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the active character is launched, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches a falling slash in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the active character is launched, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches a falling slash in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Defensive Assist: Frostveil Suppression<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the on-field character is about to be attacked, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Parries the enemy's attack, dealing massive Daze.<br/>This skill excels at parrying enemy attacks and reduces the consumption of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Points</span> when the character is under intense attacks.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the on-field character is about to be attacked, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Parries the enemy's attack, dealing massive Daze.<br/>This skill excels at parrying enemy attacks and reduces the consumption of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Points</span> when the character is under intense attacks.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Assist Follow-Up: Frostlight Reflection<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> after a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Defensive Assist</span> to activate:<br/>Launch multiple slashes in front, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, if <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are maxed out, all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are consumed to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill while in any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> is triggered. If a squadmate is then switched in via <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, Zhao automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span> and begins charging.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> after a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Defensive Assist</span> to activate:<br/>Launch multiple slashes in front, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, if <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are maxed out, all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are consumed to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill while in any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> is triggered. If a squadmate is then switched in via <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, Zhao automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span> and begins charging.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
