            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Shatterfrost Surge<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches a forward slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, consumes 5% of current HP to grant all squad members HP regeneration equal to <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">1.72%</span> of Zhao's Max HP per second for 5s. The HP-consuming effects of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Shatterfrost Surge</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Frostflow Tundra</span> can trigger at most once every 30s.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches a forward slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, consumes 5% of current HP to grant all squad members HP regeneration equal to <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">1.72%</span> of Zhao's Max HP per second for 5s. The HP-consuming effects of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Shatterfrost Surge</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Frostflow Tundra</span> can trigger at most once every 30s.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Frostflow Tundra<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches multiple forward slashes, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, consumes 5% of current HP to grant all squad members HP regeneration equal to <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">1.72%</span> of Zhao's Max HP per second for 5s. The HP-consuming effects of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Shatterfrost Surge</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Frostflow Tundra</span> can trigger at most once every 30s.<br/>Upon activating this skill, gain 20 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span>. If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are maxed out, all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are consumed to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill while in any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> is triggered. If a squadmate is then switched in via <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, Zhao automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span> and begins charging.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches multiple forward slashes, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #98EFF0\">Ice DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, consumes 5% of current HP to grant all squad members HP regeneration equal to <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">1.72%</span> of Zhao's Max HP per second for 5s. The HP-consuming effects of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Shatterfrost Surge</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Frostflow Tundra</span> can trigger at most once every 30s.<br/>Upon activating this skill, gain 20 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span>. If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are maxed out, all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are consumed to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill while in any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> is triggered. If a squadmate is then switched in via <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, Zhao automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Final Verdict</span> and begins charging.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
