        "coreSkill": {
            "desc": [
                "<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2.5 text-sm leading-4\"><!--[--><div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Core Passive: Ideal Colleague<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Zhao gains bonus CRIT Rate based on her initial Max HP, gaining <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">1.4%</span> CRIT Rate for every 1,000 initial Max HP.<br/>Upon entering the battlefield, Zhao gains 100 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span>. This effect can trigger once every 180s in Investigation Zone mode. The maximum amount of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> is 100.<br/>When the currently active character's attacks hit an enemy, Zhao gains 6 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span>. This can be triggered once every 3s.<br/>When <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are maxed out, switching Zhao to the field while in combat will activate her <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Entry Skill</span>.<br/>When Zhao activates her <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Entry Skill</span>, all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frostbite Points</span> are consumed to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>.<br/>While <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> is active, all squad members gain 5% Max HP for 40s. Re-activating <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> ends the existing instance before applying a new <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>.<br/>When Zhao activates <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, all squad members' ATK increase by <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">1,000</span> for 50s. Repeated triggers reset the duration.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div><div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Additional Ability: Crystallization<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When another character in your squad is an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Anomaly</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Support</span> character:<br/>When Zhao is within any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, the whole squad's DMG increases by 10%. If Zhao's initial Max HP exceeds 15,000, every additional 400 initial Max HP increases this DMG bonus by an additional 1%, up to a total maximum increase of 40%. This bonus reaches its maximum when Zhao's initial Max HP reaches 27,000.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div><!--]--><!-- --></div>"
            ],
            "coreGrowthStat": {
                "11102": 60000,
                "12101": 25
            }
        }
    },
