            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Shadow-Ignition<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Swiftly retreat, then attack forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>While retreating, a Perfect Dodge can be triggered, but cannot be followed up with a Dodge Counter.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Swiftly retreat, then attack forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>While retreating, a Perfect Dodge can be triggered, but cannot be followed up with a Dodge Counter.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Ink Manifestation<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, press or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Charge continuously, and release <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to launch an upward wing attack, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>While charging, incoming attacks are automatically blocked and will activate the upward wing attack.<br/>If hit at the exact moment charging begins, it triggers a Perfect Block effect, negating the DMG and increasing the skill's Interrupt Level to match a Heavy Defensive Assist, and recovering 10 Adrenaline.<br/>When an upward wing strike hits an enemy with a red flash or yellow flash, a Perfect Block can be triggered, negating the hit and increasing the skill's Interrupt Level to match a Defensive Assist and recovering 10 Adrenaline.<br/>The Perfect Block effect can occur at most once every 0.5s.<br/>If charged until flashing or when triggering the Perfect Block effect, the upward wing attack can be followed by an additional Talisman Attack.<br/>After the skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to launch EX Special Attack: Celestial Cloud Blitz - Break.<br/>After EX Special Attack: Celestial Cloud Blitz - Break, and with enough Adrenaline, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to consume another 20 Adrenaline to launch EX Special Attack: Qingming Eruption - Break.<br/>After using EX Special Attack: Qingming Eruption - Break and with enough Auric\u00a0Ink Points, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly follow up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Auric Array</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable during the upward wing attack, and Anti-Interrupt Level is increased while charging.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, press or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Charge continuously, and release <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to launch an upward wing attack, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>While charging, incoming attacks are automatically blocked and will activate the upward wing attack.<br/>If hit at the exact moment charging begins, it triggers a Perfect Block effect, negating the DMG and increasing the skill's Interrupt Level to match a Heavy Defensive Assist, and recovering 10 Adrenaline.<br/>When an upward wing strike hits an enemy with a red flash or yellow flash, a Perfect Block can be triggered, negating the hit and increasing the skill's Interrupt Level to match a Defensive Assist and recovering 10 Adrenaline.<br/>The Perfect Block effect can occur at most once every 0.5s.<br/>If charged until flashing or when triggering the Perfect Block effect, the upward wing attack can be followed by an additional Talisman Attack.<br/>After the skill, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to launch EX Special Attack: Celestial Cloud Blitz - Break.<br/>After EX Special Attack: Celestial Cloud Blitz - Break, and with enough Adrenaline, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to consume another 20 Adrenaline to launch EX Special Attack: Qingming Eruption - Break.<br/>After using EX Special Attack: Qingming Eruption - Break and with enough Auric\u00a0Ink Points, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly follow up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Auric Array</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable during the upward wing attack, and Anti-Interrupt Level is increased while charging.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Cloud-Shaper<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Continuously charge up, channeling energy around enemies to deal DMG over time, up to a max of 2s, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>Once fully charged or if interrupted, automatically trigger EX Special Attack: Ashen Ink Becomes Shadows.<br/>At the moment the skill is activated, a Perfect Dodge can be triggered. After the Perfect Dodge, enter the Vital View state.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Continuously charge up, channeling energy around enemies to deal DMG over time, up to a max of 2s, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>Once fully charged or if interrupted, automatically trigger EX Special Attack: Ashen Ink Becomes Shadows.<br/>At the moment the skill is activated, a Perfect Dodge can be triggered. After the Perfect Dodge, enter the Vital View state.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Ashen Ink Becomes Shadows<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Triggers automatically during EX Special Attack: Cloud-Shaper:<br/>When the energy orb appears and contracts, it deals <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Triggers automatically during EX Special Attack: Cloud-Shaper:<br/>When the energy orb appears and contracts, it deals <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
