            "3": {
                "skillId": 3,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Chain Attack: Auric Ink Rush<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>Rapidly dash forward and attack, followed by an explosive wing burst, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>Rapidly dash forward and attack, followed by an explosive wing burst, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Ultimate: Qingming Skyshade<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Decibel Rating is at <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Maximum</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launch a barrage of wing attacks, then guide countless talismans to attack, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, Yixuan evenly redistributes the squad's HP.<br/>After using this skill and with enough Auric Ink Points, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly follow up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Auric Array</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Decibel Rating is at <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Maximum</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launch a barrage of wing attacks, then guide countless talismans to attack, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, Yixuan evenly redistributes the squad's HP.<br/>After using this skill and with enough Auric Ink Points, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly follow up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Auric Array</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Ultimate: Endless Talisman Suppression<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Technique Points, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Consumes 120 Technique Points to spread her wings, then guide countless talismans to attack, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>With both enough Technique Points and Decibels, this skill triggers with priority.<br/>After using this skill and with enough Auric Ink Points, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly follow up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Auric Array</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, Yixuan evenly redistributes the squad's HP.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Technique Points, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Consumes 120 Technique Points to spread her wings, then guide countless talismans to attack, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Auric\u00a0Ink DMG</span>.<br/>With both enough Technique Points and Decibels, this skill triggers with priority.<br/>After using this skill and with enough Auric Ink Points, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly follow up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Auric Array</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, Yixuan evenly redistributes the squad's HP.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
