                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Penetrating Shock<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Perform up to five slashes ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>On the 3rd hit of the Basic Attack, enemies are continuously pulled in.<br/>After the 4th attack hits the enemy, repeatedly press or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly pass through enemies in front up to 5 times.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Perform up to five slashes ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>On the 3rd hit of the Basic Attack, enemies are continuously pulled in.<br/>After the 4th attack hits the enemy, repeatedly press or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly pass through enemies in front up to 5 times.<!-- --></span>"
