            "2": {
                "skillId": 2,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Dodge: Strobe<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>A quick dash dodge.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/5161803192951478865_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>A quick dash dodge.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Dash Attack: Torrent<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> during a dodge to activate:<br/>Perform a horizontal slash forward, then follow up with a thrust attack, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> during a dodge to activate:<br/>Perform a horizontal slash forward, then follow up with a thrust attack, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Dodge Counter: Ground Flash Counter<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> during a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> to activate:<br/>Perform consecutive slashes at enemies in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>. On hit, gain the Voltage Overload state for 15s. Repeated triggers refresh the duration.<br/>While in the Voltage Overload state, dodge performance is enhanced. Additionally, when using Basic Attack/Dash Attack/Dodge Counter, if the enemy target has <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span>, pressing <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> will immediately cancel the current skill and launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Azure Flash</span>.<br/>While in this state, if the enemy does not have <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to directly launch EX Special Attack: Sundering Bolt.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> during a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> to activate:<br/>Perform consecutive slashes at enemies in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>. On hit, gain the Voltage Overload state for 15s. Repeated triggers refresh the duration.<br/>While in the Voltage Overload state, dodge performance is enhanced. Additionally, when using Basic Attack/Dash Attack/Dodge Counter, if the enemy target has <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span>, pressing <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> will immediately cancel the current skill and launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Azure Flash</span>.<br/>While in this state, if the enemy does not have <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to directly launch EX Special Attack: Sundering Bolt.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
