            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Celestial Thunder<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Dash diagonally forward, then unleash a cross slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Dash diagonally forward, then unleash a cross slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Azure Flash<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Soldier 0 - Anby's attacks hit an enemy, they apply the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Silver Star</span> mark and charges the target <br/>For every one-third of charge, the enemy receives 1 stack of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span>, stacking up to 3 times.<br/>When the enemy has <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Quickly dash forward, slashing through enemies and dealing multiple hits of <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>When the skill hits an enemy, it will consume 1 stack of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span> to trigger an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span> that deals 1 extra instance of <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Soldier 0 - Anby's attacks hit an enemy, they apply the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Silver Star</span> mark and charges the target <br/>For every one-third of charge, the enemy receives 1 stack of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span>, stacking up to 3 times.<br/>When the enemy has <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Quickly dash forward, slashing through enemies and dealing multiple hits of <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>When the skill hits an enemy, it will consume 1 stack of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span> to trigger an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span> that deals 1 extra instance of <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Thunder Smite<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the additional damage from <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span> triggers 3 times on the same enemy:<br/>A lightning strike will fall at the enemy's location, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span> to enemies within range.<br/>This DMG is considered <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span> DMG.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the additional damage from <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">White Thunder</span> triggers 3 times on the same enemy:<br/>A lightning strike will fall at the enemy's location, dealing <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span> to enemies within range.<br/>This DMG is considered <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span> DMG.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Azure Flash - Boundary<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Thunder Smite</span> DMG is triggered:<br/>If EX Special Attack: Sundering Bolt or Special Attack: Azure Flash is currently being used, then <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Azure Flash - Boundary</span> will automatically trigger when the current skill ends, unleashing a flurry of slashes that deal multiple instances of <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>. This skill counts as an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Thunder Smite</span> DMG is triggered:<br/>If EX Special Attack: Sundering Bolt or Special Attack: Azure Flash is currently being used, then <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Azure Flash - Boundary</span> will automatically trigger when the current skill ends, unleashing a flurry of slashes that deal multiple instances of <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>. This skill counts as an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Sundering Bolt<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough energy, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Combines her twin swords and throws them forward for a high-speed slash, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>When the skill hits an enemy, it will fully charge <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Silver Star</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough energy, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Combines her twin swords and throws them forward for a high-speed slash, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #2EB6FF\">Electric DMG</span>.<br/>When the skill hits an enemy, it will fully charge <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Silver Star</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
