            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Piercing Dawn<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Hurl the blade to strike and pass through enemies ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> can be triggered.<br/>After triggering a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to follow up with the 5th hit of a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Hurl the blade to strike and pass through enemies ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> can be triggered.<br/>After triggering a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to follow up with the 5th hit of a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Aurora Thrust - Northern Cross<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough energy, drag the joystick forward and press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>A thrust attack that goes through enemies ahead, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Activating the skill can trigger <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> and restores 10 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Blade Etiquette</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough energy, drag the joystick forward and press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>A thrust attack that goes through enemies ahead, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Activating the skill can trigger <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> and restores 10 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Blade Etiquette</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Aurora Thrust - Southern Cross<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough energy, and without moving the joystick or when dragging it backwards, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Back away with a slash, then thrust forward, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Activating the skill can trigger <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> and restores 10 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Blade Etiquette</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough energy, and without moving the joystick or when dragging it backwards, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Back away with a slash, then thrust forward, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Activating the skill can trigger <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> and restores 10 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Blade Etiquette</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
