            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Sonic Pressure-Point Strike<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Delivers a forward melee technique while tossing firecrackers, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Delivers a forward melee technique while tossing firecrackers, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Touch of Death<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Break Force</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/>to activate:<br/><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Touch of Death</span> attacks centered on the enemy, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>The skill can be chained up to three times. Each use of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Touch of Death</span> consumes 1 point of Break Force.<br/>When Pan Yinhu is the active character, DMG received during the skill is reduced by 40% and Anti-Interrupt Level is increased. If he isn't the active character, he becomes Invulnerable.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Break Force</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/>to activate:<br/><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Touch of Death</span> attacks centered on the enemy, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>The skill can be chained up to three times. Each use of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Touch of Death</span> consumes 1 point of Break Force.<br/>When Pan Yinhu is the active character, DMG received during the skill is reduced by 40% and Anti-Interrupt Level is increased. If he isn't the active character, he becomes Invulnerable.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Mountainous Pulse Strike<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Mountainous Pulse Strike</span> unleashes a powerful strike forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Gain 3 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Break Force</span> on activation. Upon hitting an enemy, it triggers the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> of the previous character in the squad.<br/>Agents who enter the field via this Quick Assist will gain the Sheer Force bonus from the Core Passive. After switching out, Pan Yinhu will stay on the field and automatically launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Touch of Death</span> until his Break Force runs out, where he then leaves the field.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Mountainous Pulse Strike</span> unleashes a powerful strike forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Gain 3 points of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Break Force</span> on activation. Upon hitting an enemy, it triggers the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> of the previous character in the squad.<br/>Agents who enter the field via this Quick Assist will gain the Sheer Force bonus from the Core Passive. After switching out, Pan Yinhu will stay on the field and automatically launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Touch of Death</span> until his Break Force runs out, where he then leaves the field.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
