            "6": {
                "skillId": 6,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Entry Skill: Illuminating Darkness<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With 6 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> and while not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate, or press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> while in combat and switch on-field from off-field to activate:<br/>Enters the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state and activates <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Verdict</span>.<br/>Deals <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> to enemies in a large area in front.<br/>Activating this skill is considered as activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>.<br/>Enters the airborne state after using this skill.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With 6 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> and while not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate, or press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> while in combat and switch on-field from off-field to activate:<br/>Enters the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state and activates <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Verdict</span>.<br/>Deals <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> to enemies in a large area in front.<br/>Activating this skill is considered as activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>.<br/>Enters the airborne state after using this skill.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Quick Assist: Support Guard<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the active character is launched, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Leaps into the air and thrusts forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the active character is launched, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Leaps into the air and thrusts forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Assist Follow-Up: Cease Hostility<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> after a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Defensive Assist</span> to activate:<br/>Deals massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> after a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Defensive Assist</span> to activate:<br/>Deals massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Defensive Assist: When I Return<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the on-field character is about to be attacked, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Parries the enemy's attack, dealing massive Daze.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When the on-field character is about to be attacked, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Parries the enemy's attack, dealing massive Daze.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Quick Assist: Enlightened Mind - Tactical Support<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, when the active character is launched, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches a forward slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, when the active character is launched, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2454651411643363052_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches a forward slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Assist Follow-Up: Enlightened Mind - Unification<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state and after a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Defensive Assist</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Deals massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state and after a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Defensive Assist</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Deals massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
