            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Guiding Tides<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>If a dodge is available, 1 dodge chance is consumed, and the action is counted as activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge</span>.<br/>If no dodge is available or a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> is not triggered, launches a quick sword energy attack that deals <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>If a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> is triggered at this time, launches a flying sword attack, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>, and immediately follow up with the 2nd hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Swiftedge</span>.<br/>Character is briefly invulnerable during the skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>If a dodge is available, 1 dodge chance is consumed, and the action is counted as activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge</span>.<br/>If no dodge is available or a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> is not triggered, launches a quick sword energy attack that deals <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>If a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> is triggered at this time, launches a flying sword attack, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>, and immediately follow up with the 2nd hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Swiftedge</span>.<br/>Character is briefly invulnerable during the skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Gale Suppression<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches a rushing slash and a flying sword attack at the enemy, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Enemy attacks can be dodged during this skill.<br/>After this skill is used, gain 1 point of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches a rushing slash and a flying sword attack at the enemy, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Enemy attacks can be dodged during this skill.<br/>After this skill is used, gain 1 point of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Enlightened Mind - Clean Exit<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state and grounded, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Performs a swift backstep slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>If a dodge is available, 1 dodge chance is consumed, and the action is counted as activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge</span>.<br/>If a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> is triggered at this time, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind - Sunderlight Maximum</span> and enter <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Vital View</span>.<br/>After this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind - Sunderlight Maximum</span> activates, it can be immediately followed up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Enlightened Mind - Skyward Ascent</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state and grounded, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Performs a swift backstep slash, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>If a dodge is available, 1 dodge chance is consumed, and the action is counted as activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge</span>.<br/>If a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Dodge</span> is triggered at this time, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to quickly activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind - Sunderlight Maximum</span> and enter <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Vital View</span>.<br/>After this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind - Sunderlight Maximum</span> activates, it can be immediately followed up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Enlightened Mind - Skyward Ascent</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Enlightened Mind - Soaring Light<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->In the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state and with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Performs quick consecutive slashes, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> while rapidly consuming <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> until none remains.<br/>The skill ends early if <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> is insufficient or if <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> is released.<br/>Ye Shunguang will not exit the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state during this skill.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->In the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state and with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Performs quick consecutive slashes, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> while rapidly consuming <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> until none remains.<br/>The skill ends early if <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> is insufficient or if <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> is released.<br/>Ye Shunguang will not exit the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state during this skill.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Enlightened Mind - Return to Dust<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->In the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> when all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> is expended to activate:<br/>Deals massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> to enemies in a large area.<br/>Ye Shunguang will not exit the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state during this skill.<br/>After using this skill, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Verdict</span> is removed and the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state ends.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->In the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> when all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> is expended to activate:<br/>Deals massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> to enemies in a large area.<br/>Ye Shunguang will not exit the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state during this skill.<br/>After using this skill, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Verdict</span> is removed and the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state ends.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
