            "3": {
                "skillId": 3,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Chain Attack: Smite the Wicked<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>Unleashes a powerful slash at enemies ahead in a large area, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>Unleashes a powerful slash at enemies ahead in a large area, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Ultimate: Chasing Storms<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Decibel Rating is at <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Maximum</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Summons a sword formation and enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, activating an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Verdict</span> while also gaining 6 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span>. This skill deals massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, if Decibels are consumed, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> while in this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state to launch an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate: Cleaving Heavens</span> that doesn't consume Decibels.<br/>Enter the airborne state after using this skill.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Decibel Rating is at <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Maximum</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Summons a sword formation and enter the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, activating an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Verdict</span> while also gaining 6 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span>. This skill deals massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating this skill, if Decibels are consumed, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> while in this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state to launch an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate: Cleaving Heavens</span> that doesn't consume Decibels.<br/>Enter the airborne state after using this skill.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Chain Attack: Enlightened Mind - Lure Thunder<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, and when a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>Unleashes a powerful slash at enemies ahead in a large area, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Ye Shunguang will not exit the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state during this skill.<br/>Enter the airborne state after using this skill.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, and when a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>Unleashes a powerful slash at enemies ahead in a large area, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>Ye Shunguang will not exit the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state during this skill.<br/>Enter the airborne state after using this skill.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Ultimate: Cleaving Heavens<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->After consuming Decibels to launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate: Chasing Storms</span> and while in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> when all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> is expended to activate:<br/>Summons a massive blade, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> to enemies.<br/>Ye Shunguang will not exit the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state during this skill.<br/>After using this skill, the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state ends, and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Verdict</span> is removed.<br/>This skill doesn't consume Decibels.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->After consuming Decibels to launch <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate: Chasing Storms</span> and while in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> or hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> when all <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Qingming Sword Force</span> is expended to activate:<br/>Summons a massive blade, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span> to enemies.<br/>Ye Shunguang will not exit the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state during this skill.<br/>After using this skill, the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Enlightened Mind</span> state ends, and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Verdict</span> is removed.<br/>This skill doesn't consume Decibels.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
