            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Return to Ashes<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Slash forward at enemies, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>If hit by an enemy during the skill, restore 20% of missing HP when unleashing the slash. The healing effects of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes - Sacrifice</span> have a shared cooldown and can trigger once every 20s.<br/>If hit by an enemy during the skill, the slash is enhanced.<br/>DMG taken is reduced by 40% while using this skill.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Slash forward at enemies, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>If hit by an enemy during the skill, restore 20% of missing HP when unleashing the slash. The healing effects of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes - Sacrifice</span> have a shared cooldown and can trigger once every 20s.<br/>If hit by an enemy during the skill, the slash is enhanced.<br/>DMG taken is reduced by 40% while using this skill.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Return to Ashes - Sacrifice<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Enter a charging state, consuming up to 10% of Max HP and gaining 100 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Blazing Heart</span>. HP consumption will at most reduce Manato's HP to 30% of Max HP.<br/>Release the button to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes</span>. If struck during the skill, the slash heals 20% of missing HP. The healing effects of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes - Sacrifice</span> have a shared cooldown and can trigger once every 20s.<br/>If hit by an enemy during the skill or if charging reaches a certain duration, the slash is enhanced.<br/>DMG taken is reduced by 40% while using this skill.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Enter a charging state, consuming up to 10% of Max HP and gaining 100 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Blazing Heart</span>. HP consumption will at most reduce Manato's HP to 30% of Max HP.<br/>Release the button to activate <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes</span>. If struck during the skill, the slash heals 20% of missing HP. The healing effects of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Special Attack: Return to Ashes - Sacrifice</span> have a shared cooldown and can trigger once every 20s.<br/>If hit by an enemy during the skill or if charging reaches a certain duration, the slash is enhanced.<br/>DMG taken is reduced by 40% while using this skill.<br/>Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Return to Ashes - Fall<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the Molten Edge state and with sufficient Adrenaline, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Jump up and unleash a falling slash on enemies in front, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating the skill, restore 33% of Max HP.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While in the Molten Edge state and with sufficient Adrenaline, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Jump up and unleash a falling slash on enemies in front, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Upon activating the skill, restore 33% of Max HP.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
