                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Orbital Combo<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Perform up to five forward strikes, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>The fifth attack is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Whim</span>, conjuring an Ethereal figure that inflicts <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span> on enemies in a circular area ahead.<br/>When in combat and not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, Lucia gains 40 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> upon using this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Whim</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
