            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Special Attack: Symphony of the Reaper - Storm<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>This Special Attack is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Whim</span>. When activated, it recreates an Ethereal figure that slashes forward in a line, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>When in combat and not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, Lucia gains 20 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> upon using this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Whim</span>. This effect can trigger once every 5s.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>This Special Attack is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Whim</span>. When activated, it recreates an Ethereal figure that slashes forward in a line, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>When in combat and not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, Lucia gains 20 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> upon using this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Whim</span>. This effect can trigger once every 5s.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Symphony of the Reaper - Daybreak<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>This EX Special Attack is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. When activated, it summons an Ethereal figure that delivers a powerful forward slash in a line, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>When Lucia uses any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>, all squad members gain the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Darkbreaker</span> state. While in <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Darkbreaker</span> state, Sheer Force increases by 12. Every 200 points of Lucia's initial Max HP grants an additional <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">7.4</span> Sheer Force. The <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Darkbreaker</span> state can increase Sheer Force by up to a maximum of <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">900</span>, lasting 20s and repeated triggers reset the duration. When Lucia's initial Max HP reaches 24,000, the above bonus effect reaches its maximum value.<br/>When any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span> deals DMG, Lucia increases the final attack's DMG by an additional <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">70%</span> of her Max HP.<br/>If she activates this EX Special Attack while in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state and under the effect of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> duration is extended by 16s.<br/>After activating her EX Special Attack, Lucia can immediately follow up with the 5th hit of her <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>If not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, Lucia gains 60 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> upon using this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Energy, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/2297531228866436950_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>This EX Special Attack is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. When activated, it summons an Ethereal figure that delivers a powerful forward slash in a line, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>When Lucia uses any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>, all squad members gain the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Darkbreaker</span> state. While in <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Darkbreaker</span> state, Sheer Force increases by 12. Every 200 points of Lucia's initial Max HP grants an additional <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">7.4</span> Sheer Force. The <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Darkbreaker</span> state can increase Sheer Force by up to a maximum of <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">900</span>, lasting 20s and repeated triggers reset the duration. When Lucia's initial Max HP reaches 24,000, the above bonus effect reaches its maximum value.<br/>When any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span> deals DMG, Lucia increases the final attack's DMG by an additional <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">70%</span> of her Max HP.<br/>If she activates this EX Special Attack while in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state and under the effect of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> duration is extended by 16s.<br/>After activating her EX Special Attack, Lucia can immediately follow up with the 5th hit of her <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack</span>.<br/>If not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, Lucia gains 60 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> upon using this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
