            "3": {
                "skillId": 3,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Chain Attack: Stage of Brilliance<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>This Chain Attack is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. When activated, it summons an Ethereal figure that pulls in enemies in a circular area ahead and deals <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>If not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, Lucia gains 40 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> upon using this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span> is triggered, select the character to activate:<br/>This Chain Attack is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. When activated, it summons an Ethereal figure that pulls in enemies in a circular area ahead and deals <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<br/>If not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, Lucia gains 40 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> upon using this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Ultimate: Charge, Great Armor!<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Decibel Rating is at Maximum, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>This Ultimate is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. When activated, Lucia summons an Ethereal figure and rides it forward in a charge. Holding a directional button allows her to steer and extend the charge, up to 3s. During the charge, Anti-Interrupt Level is increased, DMG taken is reduced by 40%, and when Lucia takes fatal DMG, she remains in battle with HP not dropping below 1.<br/>When the charge ends, Lucia unleashes a powerful strike in a large area around her, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>. A <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> is triggered when this skill hits an enemy, and after the skill is used, it leaves behind a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Starlight Convergence</span>. <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Starlight Convergence</span> lasts 8s. While inside <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Starlight Convergence</span>, the currently active character gains HP regeneration equal to <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">1.6%</span> of Lucia's Max HP per second. This effect ends 4s after leaving the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Starlight Convergence</span> or immediately when switching out.<br/>After activation, if Lucia is in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> is active, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> duration is extended by 32s.<br/>If not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, Lucia gains 100 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> upon using this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. If she is in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state when activating this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>, she will gain 100 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> and re-enter <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state the next time she exits it. This effect cannot be stacked.<br/>Character is invulnerable while performing the powerful strike.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Decibel Rating is at Maximum, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1387329758178637252_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>This Ultimate is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. When activated, Lucia summons an Ethereal figure and rides it forward in a charge. Holding a directional button allows her to steer and extend the charge, up to 3s. During the charge, Anti-Interrupt Level is increased, DMG taken is reduced by 40%, and when Lucia takes fatal DMG, she remains in battle with HP not dropping below 1.<br/>When the charge ends, Lucia unleashes a powerful strike in a large area around her, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>. A <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> is triggered when this skill hits an enemy, and after the skill is used, it leaves behind a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Starlight Convergence</span>. <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Starlight Convergence</span> lasts 8s. While inside <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Starlight Convergence</span>, the currently active character gains HP regeneration equal to <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">1.6%</span> of Lucia's Max HP per second. This effect ends 4s after leaving the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Starlight Convergence</span> or immediately when switching out.<br/>After activation, if Lucia is in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> is active, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> duration is extended by 32s.<br/>If not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, Lucia gains 100 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> upon using this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. If she is in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state when activating this <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>, she will gain 100 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> and re-enter <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state the next time she exits it. This effect cannot be stacked.<br/>Character is invulnerable while performing the powerful strike.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
