        "coreSkill": {
            "desc": [
                "<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2.5 text-sm leading-4\"><!--[--><div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Core Passive: Lost Nocturne<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When entering the battlefield, Lucia immediately gains 60 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span>. If her <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> reaches 100 upon activating a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Whim</span> or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>, she enters the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state.<br/>When entering the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, it triggers a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span> and simultaneously activates <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span>. While <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil: Wellspring</span> is active, all squad members' Max HP increase by 5%, lasting 40s. Repeated triggers extend the duration, up to a max of 300s.<br/>While Lucia is in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state, using any <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Whim</span> consumes 25 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> and upgrades it to <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. Whenever another active character's attack hits an enemy, Lucia consumes 25 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> to unleash an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span>. This <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span> is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Harmony</span>. After Lucia triggers a skill upgrade or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span> cannot be triggered for 8s.<br/>When Lucia triggers a skill upgrade or an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aftershock</span>, all squad members gain the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dreamer's Nursery Rhyme</span> state. While in <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dreamer's Nursery Rhyme</span> state, DMG dealt increases by <span style=\"color: #2BAD00\">20%</span> for 12s. Repeated triggers reset the duration.<br/>If Lucia runs out of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream Points</span> or she leaves the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, she exits the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dream</span> state.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div><div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Additional Ability: Ballad of the Long Night<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When another character in your squad is a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Rupture</span> or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Stun</span> character:<br/>When applying <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Darkbreaker</span>, additionally applies a 30% CRIT DMG increase effect.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div><!--]--><!-- --></div>"
            ],
            "coreGrowthStat": {
                "30501": 1200,
                "12101": 25
            }
        }
    },
