        "skillKit": {
            "0": {
                "skillId": 0,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Towering Peaks<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches up to four attacks in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Interrupt Level is increased during this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches up to four attacks in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Interrupt Level is increased during this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Majestic Summit<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches up to four attacks in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt Level is increased during this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/1001669963319182284_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Launches up to four attacks in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Anti-Interrupt Level is increased during this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Immolate<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state and with at least 120 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Deals <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span> to nearby enemies, then enters the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While not in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state and with at least 120 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Deals <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span> to nearby enemies, then enters the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Inflame<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While not in combat and with more than 50% HP and less than 120 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Banyue consumes HP to recover <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span>. Upon reaching 120 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span>, Banyue immediately enters the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state.<br/>Upon entering the battlefield, gain one chance to use this skill. In Investigation Zone mode, this effect can trigger once per 180s.<br/>HP consumption will at most reduce Banyue's HP to 50% of Max HP.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While not in combat and with more than 50% HP and less than 120 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Banyue consumes HP to recover <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span>. Upon reaching 120 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span>, Banyue immediately enters the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state.<br/>Upon entering the battlefield, gain one chance to use this skill. In Investigation Zone mode, this effect can trigger once per 180s.<br/>HP consumption will at most reduce Banyue's HP to 50% of Max HP.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Toppling Mountain<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Banyue is in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to consume 120 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span> and activate:<br/>Banyue hurls a massive mountain at the enemy, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>After using this move, Banyue exits the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Banyue is in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to consume 120 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Wrathful Fires</span> and activate:<br/>Banyue hurls a massive mountain at the enemy, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>After using this move, Banyue exits the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Crushing Peaks<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While Banyue is in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state and after performing two different <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attacks</span> through Basic Attack branches or quick input commands, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Banyue launches his beads forward to imprison enemies, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Banyue automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Toppling Mountain</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->While Banyue is in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state and after performing two different <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attacks</span> through Basic Attack branches or quick input commands, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Banyue launches his beads forward to imprison enemies, dealing massive <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Banyue automatically follows up with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Toppling Mountain</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
