            "1": {
                "skillId": 1,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Earth Shaker<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, can be activated in one of three ways:<br/>After the 3rd or 4th hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Towering Peaks</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>After an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>During an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Immolate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue slams the ground repeatedly, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, can be activated in one of three ways:<br/>After the 3rd or 4th hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Towering Peaks</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>After an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>During an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Immolate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue slams the ground repeatedly, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Mountain Tremor<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, can be activated in one of two ways:<br/>After the 1st or 2nd hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Majestic Summit</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>During an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Immolate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue throws a mountain, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, can be activated in one of two ways:<br/>After the 1st or 2nd hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Majestic Summit</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>During an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Immolate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue throws a mountain, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: One's Path<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, can be activated in one of three ways:<br/>After the 3rd or 4th hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Majestic Summit</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>After an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>During an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Immolate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue throws out his beads, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, can be activated in one of three ways:<br/>After the 3rd or 4th hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Majestic Summit</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>After an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>During an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Immolate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue throws out his beads, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Lion's Roar<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, can be activated in one of two ways:<br/>After the 1st or 2nd hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Towering Peaks</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>During an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Immolate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue sends out a sonic wave forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline, can be activated in one of two ways:<br/>After the 1st or 2nd hit of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Towering Peaks</span>, press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>During an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Immolate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Assist Follow-Up</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dodge Counter</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Quick Assist</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue sends out a sonic wave forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Mountain Tremor - Wrath<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline when using <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Earth Shaker</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue throws out an even larger mountain, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline when using <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: Earth Shaker</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue throws out an even larger mountain, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->EX Special Attack: Lion's Roar - Wrath<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline when using <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: One's Path</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue releases a powerful sonic wave in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->With enough Adrenaline when using <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack: One's Path</span>, quickly input <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/7092496739393777945_250_13063804.webp\"/> in sequence to activate:<br/>Banyue releases a powerful sonic wave in front, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF5521\">Fire DMG</span>.<br/>Character is invulnerable while using this skill.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Cancel<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Banyue activates an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> ALT through quick input commands, the currently activating <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> can be interrupted. Each <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> has its own Perfect Interrupt window. Interrupting an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> after its Perfect Interrupt window will not affect the interrupted <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>'s effect. Interrupting an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> during the Perfect Interrupt window is equal to triggering a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Cancel</span>.<br/>While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state and with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Mountain's Might</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Cancel</span> is easier to trigger.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->When Banyue activates an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> ALT through quick input commands, the currently activating <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> can be interrupted. Each <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> has its own Perfect Interrupt window. Interrupting an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> after its Perfect Interrupt window will not affect the interrupted <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>'s effect. Interrupting an <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span> during the Perfect Interrupt window is equal to triggering a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Cancel</span>.<br/>While in the <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Visage of Wrath</span> state and with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Mountain's Might</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perfect Cancel</span> is easier to trigger.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
