                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Mischief Meteor Hammer<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to four attacks ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Unleashes up to four attacks ahead, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Naughty Cat Spotted<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->During combat, when Sunna is off-field and there are no enemies with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Cat's Gaze</span>, Bubblegum consumes 1 Claw Sharpener to automatically launch an attack, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>When any squad member activates <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, Sunna gains 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Claw Sharpeners</span>.<br/>When any squad member applies an Attribute Anomaly to an enemy, Sunna gains 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Claw Sharpener</span>. This effect can trigger at most once every 10s.<br/>Bubblegum inherits Sunna's initial ATK. Sunna can hold up to 6 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Claw Sharpeners</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->During combat, when Sunna is off-field and there are no enemies with <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Cat's Gaze</span>, Bubblegum consumes 1 Claw Sharpener to automatically launch an attack, dealing <span style=\"color: #F0D12B\">Physical DMG</span>.<br/>When any squad member activates <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ether Veil</span>, Sunna gains 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Claw Sharpeners</span>.<br/>When any squad member applies an Attribute Anomaly to an enemy, Sunna gains 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Claw Sharpener</span>. This effect can trigger at most once every 10s.<br/>Bubblegum inherits Sunna's initial ATK. Sunna can hold up to 6 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Claw Sharpeners</span>.<!-- --></span>"
