        "skillKit": {
            "0": {
                "skillId": 0,
                "desc": [
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Shooting Star Step<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Perform up to three attacks forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Press <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to activate:<br/>Perform up to three attacks forward, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>.<!-- --></span>",
                    "<div class=\"text-sm\"><h4 class=\"font-bold\"><!--[--><span><!-- -->Basic Attack: Adorable Explosive Impact<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></h4> <p><!--[--><span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to launch a charged attack, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>. Release the button at the right moment to trigger precise charging, increasing the Daze dealt by the skill by 20%.<br/>Nangong Yu can perform up to three hits. The second and third hits each must consume 50 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Downbeats</span>.<br/>After using a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, if enough <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Downbeats</span> are available, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to skip the first hit and directly perform the second and third hits, which always trigger precise charging.<br/>When Nangong Yu is the active character, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attacks</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimates</span>, and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attacks</span> do not interrupt the combo count of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Adorable Explosive Impact</span>.<br/>While charging the first hit, Anti-Interrupt Level increases and DMG taken decreases by 60%.<br/>While charging the second and third hits, the character is Invulnerable.<br/>During the dash phase of the first hit, enemy attacks can be Blocked. On a successful Block, the attack is treated as a precise charging attack.<br/>Character is invulnerable during all attacks.<!-- --></span><!--]--><!-- --></p></div>",
                    "<span class=\"text-sm leading-6 zzz-fmt\"><!-- -->Hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to launch a charged attack, dealing <span style=\"color: #FE437E\">Ether DMG</span>. Release the button at the right moment to trigger precise charging, increasing the Daze dealt by the skill by 20%.<br/>Nangong Yu can perform up to three hits. The second and third hits each must consume 50 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Downbeats</span>.<br/>After using a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attack</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate</span>, or <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attack</span>, if enough <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Downbeats</span> are available, hold <img alt=\"\" class=\"h-6 w-auto inline zzz-inline-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gachabase.net/prod/zzz/assets/15317334708392014940_250_13063804.webp\"/> to skip the first hit and directly perform the second and third hits, which always trigger precise charging.<br/>When Nangong Yu is the active character, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chain Attacks</span>, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimates</span>, and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">EX Special Attacks</span> do not interrupt the combo count of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Basic Attack: Adorable Explosive Impact</span>.<br/>While charging the first hit, Anti-Interrupt Level increases and DMG taken decreases by 60%.<br/>While charging the second and third hits, the character is Invulnerable.<br/>During the dash phase of the first hit, enemy attacks can be Blocked. On a successful Block, the attack is treated as a precise charging attack.<br/>Character is invulnerable during all attacks.<!-- --></span>"
                ],
